rows.label: qst200812_msg0001
rows.name:
Phew... You're sure going to some
trouble to heal some useless tree...

rows.label: qst200812_msg0002
rows.name:
I guess this lousy Saffronia is
a pretty big deal or somethin', eh?

rows.label: qst200812_msg0004
rows.name: Are you here to harass Hotaru again?

rows.label: qst200812_msg0005
rows.name:
You got it, kid.
I double-checked, and there's no way
the girl's not hidin' something.

rows.label: qst200812_msg0006
rows.name: I told you I don't have them!

rows.label: qst200812_msg0007
rows.name:
Heh.
Obviously you wouldn't say you have
them if you're tryin' to hide things.

rows.label: qst200812_msg0008
rows.name: So what, I should tell you I have them?

rows.label: qst200812_msg0009
rows.name: A-ha! So you do have them!

rows.label: qst200812_msg0010
rows.name:
Oh for crying out loud!
I don't know what to tell you anymore!

rows.label: qst200812_msg0011
rows.name:
I think in the end it'll come down to
another fight...

rows.label: qst200812_msg0013
rows.name:
But this time we brought more friends,
as well as a battle plan...

rows.label: qst200812_msg0014
rows.name:
This time you won't get away!
You'll tell us everythin'!
